prompt.title: Embedding for Promptbook: Orchestrating Complex LLM Applications
prompt.content: Promptbook is suitable for complex LLM-based applications, separating code from prompts, and orchestrating multiple prompts, but may not be ideal for simple single-prompt implementations or non-JavaScript/TypeScript environments.
